div.p: strtok is context-blind. It sees a Space (0x20) and blindly replaces it with a Null Terminator (0x00).

ol.li: It correctly terminates SELECT, *, and FROM.
It encounters the space inside "my table".

CRASH: It terminates the string there, splitting the quoted value into two garbage tokens:
"my (Unterminated quote)
table" (Garbage start)

g.title: Splits string by replacing delimiter with NULL byte
Space inside quotes replaced by NULL
